title: GirlHeFunny On FlightReacts Stealing Their Bars, Flakko and 16Shotem Skit, & More
description:
The boys talk about their rise on social media, King Von nod, girls, imitating rappers, blowing up on Tiktok and more!

----
0:00 Intro
0:05 - Clarifying their name, social handles and why their IG keeps getting deleted
2:56 - Why Kodak and Big Sean are their favorite rappers. Defending Big Sean
6:23 - Being from Miami. Educating Flakko about the dark side of Miami
12:22 - Kilamm on how they met in school by roasting each other
13:30 - Going viral in high school with his “Beat My Meat” videos and song remixes
16:58 - Almost getting kicked out of prom for saying “Beat My Meat” on stage
26:18 - Having a Haitian mom. Flakko refuses to believe Ross is Cuban. Black Israelites
28:00 - Getting their first big break on social media with the “Chester raps” videos in whiteface
31:24 - Experiencing backlash because of the whiteface and getting the videos removed 
33:39 - King Von commented and reposted their King Von parody video
35:50 - Addressing the situation where Flight stole his lyrics word-for-word
47:24 - Coming out with a skit of Flakko’s infamous 16ShotEm incident right after it happened
48:55 - Flakko is surprised that they all watch No Jumper. Getting recognized in public
54:36 - Flakko and the Girl He Funny guys bond over their stuttering problems
56:00 - Flakko refuses to speak his first language
57:15 - Being open to doing Wild N Out and other on-stage comedy opportunities 
59:40 - How attention from girls has changed since getting famous
1:06:20 - Taking negative comments to heart and not reading comments anymore
1:14:26 - Breaking down how they make money and how much money they have
1:18:35 - Flakko asks “Who’s the shooter?”
1:18:59 - Successfully losing a bunch of weight before coming to LA for the first time
1:21:34 - Trying to guess Flakko’s weight. Flakko tries to impress the guys with his athletic prowess
1:28:01 - Feeling like they would beat any creator team in basketball including RDC, AMP, etc. 
1:33:01 - Reacting to Deji fighting Floyd Mayweather
1:36:50 - Why do rappers keep ducking DDG? 
1:38:20 - Rejecting Flakko’s idea that the Youtube algorithm is racist
1:44:05 - New parody project ‘How Different States Rap’ Coming soon
1:46:20 - Flakko shows the guys the fake clubhouse Youngboy
1:49:18 - How Ross prepared to play Flakko in the 16ShotEm skit
1:50:40 - Having 10 doppelgangers
